 great couples.<br /><br />(I should probably also mention that this is the point that the film became less real and more fantastical with the appearance of the Tarzan tree house . ) I really dislike the first hour or so of this film a great deal and find it a great waste of time and energy . If you can come in towards the end I would recommend giving the film a try . Otherwise I would just skip the whole film and move on to the next film in the series .
