rstand why " Amazing Grace " Smith was killed . And with all these famous athletes becoming Chuck 's friends , why the father was constantly upset with his son taking a principled stand . And there was the cliché moment near the end when dad tells Chuck , " I never told you this , but I 'm proud of you . " Cue hug .
