ead . Plus Melody herself is n't such a great character either ... she 's damned annoying ! And bratty ! Not to mention what they 've done to Flounder . Ugh ... anyway if you decide to see this piece of created - mainly - for - profit - reasons , no - imagination , Eisner - sponsored c******t , I suggest maybe waiting ' till its on the Disney channel or some other tv station . Because , it 's not even worth the price of a rental.<br /><br / > * out of * * * * * stars .
